            <p>
                Really thankful to all the people who helped me make this bot!
                <ul>
                    <li>First and most foremost, I'd like to credit the devs of the <a href="https://discord.js.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">discord.js</a> library, which really simplified the development phase.</li>
                    <li>Then, we have
                        <div class="link-hover">
                            <a href="https://discordapp.com/users/800686782114693180" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">mimi</a>
                            <div class="links">
                                <div class="discord-card">
                                    <%- `<img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/${devs.mimi?.id}/${devs.mimi?.avatar}.png" alt="avatar" selectable="false">` %>
                                    <div class="discord-card-body" selectable="false">
                                        <%- `<p>${devs.mimi?.username}</p>
																					<p>#${devs.mimi?.discriminator}</p>` %>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>. Throughout the whole development phase, she constantly helped with the debugging.
                    </li>
                    <li><div class="link-hover">
                            <a href="https://discordapp.com/users/497959318310748181" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">miv</a>
                            <div class="links">
                                <div class="discord-card">
                                    <%- `<img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/${devs.miv?.id}/${devs.miv?.avatar}.png" alt="avatar" selectable="false">` %>
                                    <div class="discord-card-body" selectable="false">
                                        <%- `<p>${devs.miv?.username}</p>
																					<p>#${devs.miv?.discriminator}</p>` %>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
